div.bibl: St. Constantine Parish News, Dec. 17, 1933. [GREEK WOMEN'S UNIVERSITY CLUB]

body.p: Parish News congratulates the Greek Women's University Club on the success of their musicale last Sunday afternoon. We also wish to congratulate the participants who so successfully did their part in making this affair a success. We especially take the privilege of congratulating Nicholas Sothras and Sophia Stamos for their talent.
